Wondering what to gift your mom or dad this holiday season? Don’t sweat it. It’s easy to overthink gifts for older parents ― some gadgets seem too complicated to use, new socks and perfume feel a bit cliché ― but it doesn’t have to be. Your best bet? Give gifts that’ll make their life easier. That’s why we’ve done the hard work for you by pulling together a list of useful gifts for older parents. Take a look at our 17 favorite finds below:  HuffPost may receive a share from purchases made via links on this page.